description	"Jyn Erso

Class Summary: 
A speedy pistoleer hero with a stun gun

Weaponry:
- Truncheon (Melee weapon, cannot block attacks)
- A180 (Based on Pistol level 2, higher damage)
- A180 Ion Attachment *

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
---A180 Ion Attachment
- Based on Bowcaster level (1)
- Electrifies and knocks down enemies on direct hits
- 2 shots per clip, 14 shots total
- Magazine style reload

Attributes:
- Rally
- Immune to force sense
- Immune to Mind Trick
- Flipkick
- Heal (1)

Inventory:
- Binoculars
- Portable Sentry Gun

Abilities:
- Dodge (3)
- Dash (2)

Jyn Erso was a human female soldier and former criminal who became a pivotal member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic when she led Rogue One in stealing the Death Star plans during the Battle of Scarif."